OL,3,CControversial P&O Ferries chief
OL,4,Cexecutive Peter Hebblethwaite steps
OL,5,Cdown
OL,7,FThe controversial boss of P&O Ferries,
OL,8,Fwho led the firm's move to sack almost
OL,9,F800 workers and replace them with
OL,10,Fcheaper agency staff, is quitting.
OL,12,FP&O said Hebblethwaite had announced
OL,13,Fplans to resign to "dedicate more time
OL,14,Fto family matters".
OL,16,FThe firm and its management was widely
OL,17,Fcondemned in March 2022 when it sacked
OL,18,Fnearly 800 workers without
OL,19,Fconsultation and replaced them with
OL,20,Fagency staff on lower wages.
