OL,3,CControversial P&O Ferries chief
OL,4,Cexecutive Peter Hebblethwaite steps
OL,5,Cdown
OL,7,FMr Hebblethwaite resisted widespread
OL,8,Fcalls from ministers and trade unions
OL,9,Fto resign after admitting to MPs that
OL,10,Fthe company broke the law by not
OL,11,Fconsulting with trade unions.
OL,13,FHe also told Parliament the agency
OL,14,Fworkers' pay averaged #5.50 per hour.
OL,16,FThis was below the UK's national
OL,17,Fminimum wage at the time of #9.50 per
OL,18,Fhour, but P&O Ferries insisted it was
OL,19,Fin line with international maritime
OL,20,Flaw.
