OL,3,CControversial P&O Ferries chief
OL,4,Cexecutive Peter Hebblethwaite steps
OL,5,Cdown
OL,7,FThe move comes after ITV News reported
OL,8,Fin July that Hebblethwaite was awarded
OL,9,Fa large pay increase, even as P&O
OL,10,Fposted a loss of #91 million.
OL,12,FAs Chief Executive, Hebblethwaite was
OL,13,Fpaid #683,000 - representing an
OL,14,Fincrease of at least 55% on the
OL,15,Fearnings of P&O's highest-paid
OL,16,Fdirector in 2022.
