OL,7,FA spokesperson for P&O Ferries said:
OL,8,F"Peter Hebblethwaite has communicated
OL,9,Fhis intention to resign from his
OL,10,Fposition as chief executive officer to
OL,11,Fdedicate more time to family matters.
OL,13,F"P&O Ferries extends its gratitude to
OL,14,FPeter Hebblethwaite for his
OL,15,Fcontributions as CEO over the past
OL,16,Ffour years."
